d":2063367,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"係咪翻譯版H漫嚟？<br />\n係就屌你老母啦！難得有間會賣<br />\n信和果啲都唔見有，想買都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好講野, 人地台版黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無搭錯線<br />\n我意思係難得有一間有賣中文版嘅H漫（台譯都無問題）<br />\n咁都要比人搞有無搞撚錯"},{"pid":"602016265ec7540558f65c1c5f440da87a34eef8","tid":2063367,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:19:43.000Z","msg":"淫審處一向仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}